description: A Novel AI Programming Challenge about Lux
name: lux_ai_2021

actTimeout.description: Maximum runtime (seconds) to obtain an action from an agent.

episodeSteps.description: Maximum number of steps the environment can run. Total is this number -1. One complete game is 361 steps

runTimeout.description: Maximum runtime (seconds) of an episode (not necessarily DONE).

remainingOverageTime.description: Total remaining banked time (seconds) that can be used in excess of per-step actTimeouts -- agent is disqualified with TIMEOUT status when this drops below 0.

updates.description: List of update strings for agents to use and generate the observed state

reward.description: number of cities you own on the board

title: Lux AI Challenge: 2021
